UID:KeyKozgacDnFflMXHuLgY
SUMMARY:SAM Gallery Presents: Viewpoint
DTSTAMP:20260318T235237Z
DTSTART:20260329T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Artists invite us into artworks using perspective\, both as an 
	artistic tool that shows space\, depth and mass\, and as a way of communic
	ating their point of view. In Viewpoint\, SAM Gallery artists take us down
	 mysterious city streets\, welcome us to green spaces\, and inspire us to 
	explore surreal landscapes. Featuring the work of Katie Metz\, Elizabeth G
	ahan\, Perri Lynch Howard and more. Join us and our featured artists for a
